    <item>
      <title>英国采取紧急措施缓解监狱骚乱造成的拥挤状况</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/uk-takes-emergency-action-to-ease-prison-crowding-after-riots</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国政府已批准采取紧急措施，以防止英格兰北部监狱过度拥挤，因为该国不堪重负的刑罚制度开始接收数百名因最近的极右翼骚乱而被起诉的人。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/uk-takes-emergency-action-to-ease-prison-crowding-after-riots</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 06:16:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度最高法院介入处理医生因强奸案罢工事件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/india-s-top-court-steps-in-after-doctors-strike-over-rape-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度最高法院本周将开始审理东部城市加尔各答一名实习医生涉嫌强奸和谋杀的案件，该案件引发了全国范围的医生抗议和罢工。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/india-s-top-court-steps-in-after-doctors-strike-over-rape-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 05:49:47 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>斯塔默将面临英国日益激烈的罢工行动，这是总理的下一个考验</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/starmer-faces-growing-uk-strike-action-in-next-test-for-premier</link>
      <description><![CDATA[英国首相基尔·斯塔默 (Keir Starmer) 面临新一轮罢工浪潮，尽管结束罢工行动是其政府的首要任务，但代表医生、火车司机、地方政府工作人员和边境工作人员的英国工会组织也要求加薪。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/starmer-faces-growing-uk-strike-action-in-next-test-for-premier</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 05:26:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>习近平向越南领导人林郑月娥表示，希望建立“友谊”</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/xi-tells-vietnam-s-leader-to-lam-he-wants-to-build-friendship</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国国家主席习近平向越南总统苏林表示，他愿意同越南领导人发展良好关系。这是苏林就任国家最高领导人以来首次出访。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/xi-tells-vietnam-s-leader-to-lam-he-wants-to-build-friendship</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 04:07:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>泰国法院开始审理他信涉嫌侮辱王室的案件</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/thaksin-faces-royal-insult-trial-as-thai-court-begins-hearing</link>
      <description><![CDATA[泰国前领导人他信·西那瓦周一在曼谷一家法庭出庭，法庭开始审查针对他信的侮辱王室案件的证据。几天前，他的女儿刚刚出任这个东南亚国家的新总理。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/thaksin-faces-royal-insult-trial-as-thai-court-begins-hearing</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 03:51:13 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>日本领导人候选人及其关键政策立场</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/who-could-replace-kishida-candidates-who-could-be-japan-s-new-prime-minister</link>
      <description><![CDATA[日本首相岸田文雄上周表示，他不会参加 9 月份执政的自民党总裁选举，此后日本将迎来新领导人。由于自民党在议会中占据主导地位，自民党总裁几乎肯定会成为首相。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/who-could-replace-kishida-candidates-who-could-be-japan-s-new-prime-minister</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 02:41:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国与菲律宾船只在争议海域再次发生碰撞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/china-philippines-ships-clash-again-in-signs-of-unresolved-row</link>
      <description><![CDATA[中国与菲律宾海岸警卫队船只在南海再次发生冲突，这是争议海域的最新一次冲突，并破坏了避免冲突的临时协议。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/china-philippines-ships-clash-again-in-signs-of-unresolved-row</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 02:19:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>佐科威在最后一刻改组印尼内阁，以推动其政治遗产</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/indonesia-to-name-new-energy-minister-in-latest-cabinet-shuffle</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印尼总统佐科·维多多在其卸任前几周进行了更广泛的内阁改组，更换了国家能源和投资负责人，以确保他的政策仍然是新一届普拉博沃·苏比安托政府的优先事项。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-19/indonesia-to-name-new-energy-minister-in-latest-cabinet-shuffle</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 19 Aug 2024 00:36:44 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>政治剧影响泰铢复苏，交易员等待泰国银行转账</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/political-turmoil-threatens-baht-resurgence-as-traders-await-bot</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于本周央行政策会议召开前市场正在消化泰铢最新的政治戏剧，泰铢近期的涨势面临威胁。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-18/political-turmoil-threatens-baht-resurgence-as-traders-await-bot</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 18 Aug 2024 21:32:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
